text: We propose a hybrid neural network model that integrates LSTM and Transformer blocks to improve long-range language modeling performance on academic corpora.
This study explores the effects of climate change on marine biodiversity, with a focus on coral bleaching events in the Pacific Ocean.
Our experiment applies CRISPR-Cas9 to engineer drought-resistant rice strains, analyzing yield improvement under controlled environmental conditions.
This paper presents a blockchain-based framework to enhance data security in supply chain logistics across international borders.
A novel unsupervised clustering technique is introduced to detect financial fraud using transactional metadata and temporal behavior features.
We investigate the relationship between adolescent mental health and social media usage using a longitudinal survey across three countries.
This research introduces an AI-powered diagnostic assistant for early detection of Alzheimer's disease using speech analysis and memory tests.
The paper studies energy-efficient routing protocols in wireless sensor networks deployed in smart agricultural systems.
We analyze the ethical implications of deepfake technology in political campaigns and propose a regulatory framework for digital authenticity.
A comparative analysis of machine learning models for predicting stock price volatility based on macroeconomic indicators is conducted.
